import React from 'react'
import { Box, Container, Text } from '@chakra-ui/react'

export default function Home() {
  return (
  <Container maxW='xl' centerContent>
    <Box
    d="flex"
    justifyContent="center"
    p={3}
    bg={"white"}
    w='100%'
    m="40px 0 15px 0"
    borderRadius='lg'
    borderWidth="1px"
    >
      <Text>
        Chat Buddy
      </Text>
    </Box>
    <Box></Box>

  </Container>
  )
}
